<plot>Two FBI agents, Mike Tozzi (Noth) and Cuthbert Gibbons (Meaney), try to bring down a loan-sharking business run by the mob. Things become increasingly intense after a series of crosses and double-crosses leave both agents at the mercy of their targets. But that doesn't prevent the sexual tension from heating up, as one of the agents (Noth) gets tangled up with his informant(James Villemaire)'s sister (Dagmara Dominczyk).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?055728</url></doc>
